WEBVTT

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:19.450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}The Apothecary Diaries</b></font>

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:19.450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}The Apothecary <font color="#000000">Diaries</font></b></font>

00:01:32.860 --> 00:01:35.860
<font size="10">{\an1}This story is a work of fiction. The names of all of the characters, organizations, and so on
 are imaginary. It also bears no connection to any specific real-life events.</font>

00:01:44.930 --> 00:01:45.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Mother?</font>

00:01:57.730 --> 00:02:01.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Why did my mother have that look on her face?</i></font>

00:02:04.430 --> 00:02:06.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Now, return to your room.</font>

00:02:07.230 --> 00:02:08.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Y-Yes.</font>

00:02:13.160 --> 00:02:19.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That old man... That old woman... 
Who were they?</i></font>

00:02:23.950 --> 00:02:25.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's hard to recall...</i></font>

00:02:37.070 --> 00:02:38.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What an awful dream.</font>

00:02:46.840 --> 00:02:52.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Back then, I had no way of knowing 
who the old man and old woman were.</i></font>

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:53.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>They taught me later.</i></font>

00:02:53.970 --> 00:02:57.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The old man was my father 
and the old woman was my grandmother.</i></font>

00:02:57.470 --> 00:02:58.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Also...</i></font>

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:03.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>They told me that the man I always thought 
was my father was actually my brother.</i></font>

00:03:07.700 --> 00:03:10.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That girl can be very dull 
in strangely specific instances,</i></font>

00:03:10.140 --> 00:03:11.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but she's bound to figure this out soon.</i></font>

00:03:12.710 --> 00:03:14.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Or, perhaps she already has...</i></font>

00:03:15.160 --> 00:03:17.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That would put me at ease.</i></font>

00:03:17.570 --> 00:03:20.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I can't stay quiet about this forever.</font>

00:03:28.570 --> 00:03:32.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A long time ago, this land was inhabited 
by a different group of people.</font>

00:03:33.270 --> 00:03:37.230
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}<font size="18">Episode 31: The Shrine of Choosing</font></font>

00:03:33.570 --> 00:03:40.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}These people had no leader, but a noble
 woman arrived from a distant land.</font>

00:03:40.210 --> 00:03:43.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The woman became pregnant 
with the child from the heavens.</font>

00:03:43.760 --> 00:03:47.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That child became the first emperor of Li.</font>

00:03:47.710 --> 00:03:51.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The woman, whose eyes could see 
even in the darkest of nights,</font>

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:53.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">later became known as the Mother Royal.</font>

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:57.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Some say she was a sorceress who 
descended from the land of sorcerers.</font>

00:03:57.550 --> 00:04:00.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The fable of this nation's founding, huh?</i></font>

00:04:00.510 --> 00:04:02.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How is it, apothecary?</font>

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:04.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Careful, Master Jinshi, 
or they'll see your face.</font>

00:04:05.020 --> 00:04:06.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oops.</font>

00:04:06.100 --> 00:04:08.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>They're so nicely focused 
on their studies right now.</i></font>

00:04:08.460 --> 00:04:11.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The appearance of this creature 
would steal their attention.</i></font>

00:04:11.990 --> 00:04:13.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, there are around twenty students?</font>

00:04:14.750 --> 00:04:17.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I was hoping we would get more.</font>

00:04:17.370 --> 00:04:20.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We started with about ten, so it is increasing.</font>

00:04:20.400 --> 00:04:24.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Well, it sounds about right, 
I think. That said...</i></font>

00:04:24.770 --> 00:04:29.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If Master Jinshi's plan works out and 
more servant girls become literate,</i></font>

00:04:29.500 --> 00:04:31.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>the nature of the rear palace 
should begin to change.</i></font>

00:04:32.460 --> 00:04:37.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>In fact, Xiaolan is already beginning 
to read simple stories by herself.</i></font>

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:40.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi, we must move on.</font>

00:04:40.930 --> 00:04:43.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yeah. What about you?</font>

00:04:43.850 --> 00:04:46.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I will stay and observe a bit more.</font>

00:04:46.750 --> 00:04:50.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see. If you notice anything, report to me.</font>

00:04:50.290 --> 00:04:51.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Understood.</font>

00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:53.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Xiaolan.</font>

00:04:54.450 --> 00:04:57.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey! I didn't notice you, Maomao!</font>

00:04:57.740 --> 00:05:00.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How is it? Have you learned a few characters?</font>

00:05:01.270 --> 00:05:05.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh, only a few! I still have 
to ask the teacher about some.</font>

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:06.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Come with me, Maomao!</font>

00:05:06.450 --> 00:05:07.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh, sure.</font>

00:05:07.420 --> 00:05:12.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The teacher is in the building next door. 
I visit him sometimes to ask questions.</font>

00:05:12.550 --> 00:05:15.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Hmm? Is that an old shrine?</i></font>

00:05:15.580 --> 00:05:19.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Excuse me! Coming in!</font>

00:05:19.190 --> 00:05:23.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, yes. You there, 
young lady, you're a new face.</font>

00:05:31.140 --> 00:05:34.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's strangely thin and long, 
and goes quite deep, it seems.</i></font>

00:05:35.540 --> 00:05:40.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The distance between the pillars is short. 
It must be divided up into quite a few rooms.</i></font>

00:05:41.490 --> 00:05:43.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Does that shrine interest you?</font>

00:05:43.820 --> 00:05:48.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, it seems like a strangely-shaped building.</font>

00:05:48.020 --> 00:05:52.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's a shrine built by the people 
who originally lived here.</font>

00:05:52.460 --> 00:05:57.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">When the Mother Royal ruled over this place, 
she didn't denounce the old religion.</font>

00:05:57.700 --> 00:05:59.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is the Mother Royal
 the first emperor's mother</font>

00:05:59.580 --> 00:06:01.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">that was in that story from earlier?</font>

00:06:02.110 --> 00:06:05.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. The Mother Royal told her son this:</font>

00:06:06.510 --> 00:06:11.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">"The one who rules this land 
must pass through that shrine.</font>

00:06:11.690 --> 00:06:16.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Only those who choose the right path 
can be the ruler of this land."</font>

00:06:16.620 --> 00:06:21.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The son successfully passed through 
that shrine to become the emperor.</font>

00:06:21.900 --> 00:06:25.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The capital city was moved to 
this region because of that shrine, too.</font>

00:06:25.730 --> 00:06:26.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wow!</font>

00:06:26.820 --> 00:06:29.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But the shrine hasn't been 
used in many decades.</font>

00:06:29.940 --> 00:06:32.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I wonder if it will ever be used again.</font>

00:06:33.460 --> 00:06:35.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What do you mean?</font>

00:06:35.090 --> 00:06:40.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The previous emperor's elder brothers 
all passed away from an epidemic.</font>

00:06:41.620 --> 00:06:44.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Only the previous emperor survived.</font>

00:06:44.210 --> 00:06:48.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>In other words, there was no need to do 
the rite of passage to determine the heir.</i></font>

00:06:48.510 --> 00:06:54.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm glad someone is showing interest 
in that shrine. It's truly been a while.</font>

00:06:54.320 --> 00:06:57.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Did it attract more attention in the past?</font>

00:06:57.320 --> 00:07:01.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. There was a quirky doctor 
who used to work here.</font>

00:07:01.400 --> 00:07:05.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He would wander around the rear 
palace whenever he had the time.</font>

00:07:05.260 --> 00:07:08.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He asked about the shrine, 
like you did just now—</font>

00:07:08.020 --> 00:07:09.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is that Luomen...?</font>

00:07:09.630 --> 00:07:10.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do you know him?</font>

00:07:11.320 --> 00:07:13.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Oops. I didn't mean to...</i></font>

00:07:13.840 --> 00:07:15.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He's my adopted father.</font>

00:07:15.020 --> 00:07:16.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">After he left the rear palace,</font>

00:07:16.370 --> 00:07:18.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">he began working as an apothecary
 in the pleasure district.</font>

00:07:18.840 --> 00:07:21.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see. You're Luomen's...</font>

00:07:22.200 --> 00:07:26.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I wonder if he got along with my dad?</i></font>

00:07:26.010 --> 00:07:26.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao!</font>

00:07:27.320 --> 00:07:29.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Look! I wrote something!</font>

00:07:29.440 --> 00:07:30.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wow.</font>

00:07:33.150 --> 00:07:34.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There is no poison.</font>

00:07:36.590 --> 00:07:38.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I will take my leave now.</font>

00:07:38.160 --> 00:07:39.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wait, apothecary.</font>

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:42.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm going somewhere after this, 
and I want you to accompany me.</font>

00:07:43.400 --> 00:07:44.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Where to?</font>

00:07:44.800 --> 00:07:46.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">To the Shrine of Choosing.</font>

00:07:48.740 --> 00:07:51.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why are you doing this all of a sudden?</font>

00:07:51.070 --> 00:07:53.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What is he planning to do?</i></font>

00:07:54.670 --> 00:07:56.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's the old shrine that I saw today.</i></font>

00:07:57.500 --> 00:07:58.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>And...</i></font>

00:07:58.660 --> 00:08:00.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Is that the teacher from the school?</i></font>

00:08:00.780 --> 00:08:02.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I have eagerly awaited your arrival.</font>

00:08:02.910 --> 00:08:05.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">May I attempt this again?</font>

00:08:06.080 --> 00:08:10.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You might get the same result, 
but if that's acceptable, it's fine.</font>

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:14.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What a way to speak to the emperor.</i></font>

00:08:14.100 --> 00:08:15.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Who will be accompanying you?</font>

00:08:15.860 --> 00:08:18.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hmm. I will take these two.</font>

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:19.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh?</font>

00:08:19.550 --> 00:08:22.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Um, isn't this place off-limits to women?</font>

00:08:23.410 --> 00:08:25.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The Mother Royal and 
Empress Dowager were women, too.</font>

00:08:26.980 --> 00:08:27.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please.</font>

00:08:27.970 --> 00:08:29.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, let's go.</font>

00:08:35.540 --> 00:08:37.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Three doors...?</i></font>

00:08:37.370 --> 00:08:42.200
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}Do not pass through the red door</b></font>

00:08:38.110 --> 00:08:41.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Do not pass through the red door?</i></font>

00:08:41.180 --> 00:08:44.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The colors of the doors 
are blue, red, and green.</i></font>

00:08:45.140 --> 00:08:47.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>So, we should choose blue or green?</i></font>

00:08:47.520 --> 00:08:50.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Which door will you choose?</font>

00:08:50.040 --> 00:08:53.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's go with the blue this time, 
since I chose green the last time.</font>

00:08:53.740 --> 00:08:57.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's true. This way, please.</font>

00:09:01.280 --> 00:09:04.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I hope you'd pay more heed to 
the ones tasked to maintain this place.</font>

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:09.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It goes unused for so long, 
then suddenly someone wants to use it.</font>

00:09:09.700 --> 00:09:11.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Haha, apologies for the trouble.</font>

00:09:13.650 --> 00:09:17.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Three doors again... Green, brown, light blue.</i></font>

00:09:17.970 --> 00:09:21.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The next one says, 
"Do not enter the brown door."</i></font>

00:09:18.660 --> 00:09:21.030
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}Do not enter the brown door</b></font>

00:09:21.380 --> 00:09:23.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'll go with green.</font>

00:09:23.050 --> 00:09:24.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>So...</i></font>

00:09:26.030 --> 00:09:29.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Is this going to go on and on like this?</i></font>

00:09:35.030 --> 00:09:38.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Up and down, going back and turning,</i></font>

00:09:38.410 --> 00:09:40.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I've lost my sense of direction.</i></font>

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:43.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Feels like we're walking around 
the same place in circles.</i></font>

00:09:44.380 --> 00:09:47.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Why did the emperor bring me along?</i></font>

00:09:48.450 --> 00:09:50.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I hope this is over soon...</i></font>

00:09:55.750 --> 00:09:57.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is the final door.</font>

00:09:58.450 --> 00:10:02.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The doors are blue, purple, and yellow.</i></font>

00:10:03.160 --> 00:10:05.660
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}Do not enter the blue door</b></font>

00:10:03.160 --> 00:10:05.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>"Do not enter the blue door."</i></font>

00:10:06.440 --> 00:10:10.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Also, there's another door 
that leads into this place.</i></font>

00:10:10.220 --> 00:10:12.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I guess a separate path converges here.</i></font>

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:14.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I've decided.</font>

00:10:15.190 --> 00:10:16.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I choose the yellow.</font>

00:10:18.740 --> 00:10:20.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you certain?</font>

00:10:20.450 --> 00:10:21.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please.</font>

00:10:24.700 --> 00:10:26.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>A dead end.</i></font>

00:10:26.180 --> 00:10:30.190
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#2b2d27">Child of royalty, yet not
 child of the Mother Royal</font></font></b></font>

00:10:26.840 --> 00:10:30.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>"Child of royalty, 
yet not child of the Mother Royal?"</i></font>

00:10:30.690 --> 00:10:34.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I have no idea what that means, 
but it's definitely a rejection of some sort.</i></font>

00:10:34.060 --> 00:10:36.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Same result as before.</font>

00:10:41.260 --> 00:10:43.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Why is he so serious?</i></font>

00:10:44.080 --> 00:10:47.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I guess I am incapable of 
deciphering the will of the heavens.</font>

00:10:47.230 --> 00:10:49.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I must disagree.</font>

00:10:49.490 --> 00:10:52.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">When you included this shrine 
into the rear palace,</font>

00:10:52.960 --> 00:10:56.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I became the only person to manage this place.</font>

00:10:56.700 --> 00:10:59.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What value could there be 
in the will of the heavens?</font>

00:10:59.660 --> 00:11:03.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>This old eunuch must have been 
managing this old shrine</i></font>

00:11:03.930 --> 00:11:06.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>from way before the rear palace was built.</i></font>

00:11:06.610 --> 00:11:11.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>He even accepted castration to become 
a eunuch so he could remain here...</i></font>

00:11:12.780 --> 00:11:14.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The exit is this way.</font>

00:11:20.020 --> 00:11:25.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The emperor followed every direction. 
He didn't seem to make any mistakes.</i></font>

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:27.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Yet he wasn't able to reach the correct answer.</i></font>

00:11:28.940 --> 00:11:31.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Was there some other intent behind this?</i></font>

00:11:31.620 --> 00:11:35.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The number of rooms? 
The color of the doors chosen?</i></font>

00:11:35.010 --> 00:11:38.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Luomen probably would have figured it out.</font>

00:11:38.700 --> 00:11:40.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Dad would have...?</i></font>

00:11:40.700 --> 00:11:43.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you saying my adopted 
father would understand?</font>

00:11:43.200 --> 00:11:45.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, I can't say for certain.</font>

00:11:46.120 --> 00:11:48.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's true that Dad has 
an astonishing amount of knowledge.</i></font>

00:11:49.310 --> 00:11:52.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That said, being told that 
I can't do it is a bit annoying.</i></font>

00:11:53.410 --> 00:11:57.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Dad's knowledge is exceptionally 
advanced in the field of medicine.</i></font>

00:11:57.710 --> 00:11:59.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Is that somehow related to this?</i></font>

00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:11.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Three doors, three colors.</i></font>

00:12:11.080 --> 00:12:16.210
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#2b2d27">Child of royalty, yet not
 child of the Mother Royal</font></font></b></font>

00:12:12.150 --> 00:12:15.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>"Child of royalty, 
yet not child of the Mother Royal."</i></font>

00:12:15.710 --> 00:12:18.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What does that phrase mean?</i></font>

00:12:23.660 --> 00:12:27.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do you have any idea what 
"not child of the Mother Royal" could mean?</font>

00:12:28.450 --> 00:12:29.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Now that I think about it,</i></font>

00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:37.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>in the foundation story, only the Mother 
Royal appears, not the father.</i></font>

00:12:37.270 --> 00:12:38.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>One might think, then, that we would</i></font>

00:12:38.730 --> 00:12:40.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>adopt a system that values 
the maternal bloodline,</i></font>

00:12:40.780 --> 00:12:44.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>yet our nation is based on a paternal 
hereditary succession system.</i></font>

00:12:44.680 --> 00:12:48.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Given that, if one were to devise a way 
to carry on the Mother Royal's bloodline...</i></font>

00:12:48.580 --> 00:12:52.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The previous emperor's elder brothers 
all passed away from an epidemic.</font>

00:12:53.460 --> 00:12:54.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi.</font>

00:12:55.020 --> 00:12:56.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Did you notice something?</font>

00:12:57.130 --> 00:13:00.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Were all the previous emperor's 
siblings born to the same mother?</font>

00:13:01.020 --> 00:13:06.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Not everyone, but I heard the mothers 
who gave birth to the princes were sisters.</font>

00:13:06.650 --> 00:13:09.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In other words,
 they were of close bloodlines.</font>

00:13:10.920 --> 00:13:15.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This may sound rude, but might I speak freely?</font>

00:13:15.370 --> 00:13:17.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I will allow it. Go on.</font>

00:13:18.030 --> 00:13:24.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Did several of the previous 
emperors have poor eyesight?</font>

00:13:26.110 --> 00:13:29.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I have heard once that many 
did not possess the best eyesight.</font>

00:13:29.690 --> 00:13:32.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The previous emperor could 
see perfectly well, though.</font>

00:13:32.330 --> 00:13:33.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I knew it.</i></font>

00:13:34.170 --> 00:13:37.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Could we go through the shrine again?</font>

00:13:37.880 --> 00:13:41.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do you think you're worthy, young lady?</font>

00:13:42.100 --> 00:13:46.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I allowed you to enter this last time, but it 
wouldn't do to permit too many attempts.</font>

00:13:46.840 --> 00:13:50.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's especially true if you're going to 
opine on the doors to choose.</font>

00:13:50.900 --> 00:13:54.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You are neither a concubine 
nor a princess, are you?</font>

00:13:54.670 --> 00:13:56.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Nope, just a servant girl.</i></font>

00:13:56.560 --> 00:14:00.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hmm. Well, I could accept her as a concubine.</font>

00:14:00.380 --> 00:14:03.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'd have trouble convincing Lakan, though.</font>

00:14:03.070 --> 00:14:04.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Surely you jest...</i></font>

00:14:04.970 --> 00:14:08.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Surely you jest! There's no telling 
what the other concubines would think!</font>

00:14:09.720 --> 00:14:10.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's a good point, as well.</font>

00:14:11.640 --> 00:14:14.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Then maybe you should take her.</font>

00:14:15.910 --> 00:14:17.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Would that be acceptable?</font>

00:14:17.710 --> 00:14:20.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If that is your wish.</font>

00:14:20.990 --> 00:14:22.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, let's go.</font>

00:14:23.880 --> 00:14:26.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>He's more playful than usual.</i></font>

00:14:27.980 --> 00:14:31.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">First, the blue, red, and green doors.</font>

00:14:31.640 --> 00:14:34.390
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}Do not pass through the red door</b></font>

00:14:32.090 --> 00:14:34.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>"Do not pass through the red door."</i></font>

00:14:34.740 --> 00:14:36.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Which would you choose?</font>

00:14:36.130 --> 00:14:36.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The blue one.</font>

00:14:37.470 --> 00:14:40.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The same one as the emperor, at least for now.</i></font>

00:14:42.270 --> 00:14:45.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Next is the green, brown, and light blue.</font>

00:14:45.280 --> 00:14:47.780
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}Do not pass through the brown door</b></font>

00:14:45.810 --> 00:14:47.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">"Do not pass through the brown door."</font>

00:14:48.350 --> 00:14:49.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The light blue door.</font>

00:14:51.630 --> 00:14:55.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hmm. That's not the one I chose.</font>

00:14:56.420 --> 00:14:59.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I couldn't tell the last time I went through.</i></font>

00:14:59.230 --> 00:15:02.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If there is a door that only 
the Mother Royal's children can choose...</i></font>

00:15:03.690 --> 00:15:07.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The key would be the colors of the doors.</i></font>

00:15:09.870 --> 00:15:14.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That's the tenth one. 
White, purple, and green doors...</i></font>

00:15:14.550 --> 00:15:17.930
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}Choose the red door</b></font>

00:15:15.240 --> 00:15:17.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">"Choose the red door."</font>

00:15:17.930 --> 00:15:19.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hmm.</font>

00:15:19.150 --> 00:15:22.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's no red door. What is this?</font>

00:15:22.830 --> 00:15:24.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The green door.</font>

00:15:25.250 --> 00:15:26.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Green?</font>

00:15:27.540 --> 00:15:28.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You'll see when we get through.</font>

00:15:32.320 --> 00:15:33.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is...</font>

00:15:39.530 --> 00:15:43.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Congratulations. 
You have chosen the correct path.</font>

00:15:44.790 --> 00:15:49.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In the past, the one chosen by 
the Mother Royal became the next king.</font>

00:15:49.780 --> 00:15:54.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He would stand in this spot and 
make a proclamation to the people.</font>

00:15:54.780 --> 00:15:58.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If nobody could choose the right path,</font>

00:15:58.530 --> 00:16:04.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">they would revisit this shrine with 
a concubine who could choose the right path.</font>

00:16:04.850 --> 00:16:09.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In the past, this would be done 
by those with the right blood.</font>

00:16:09.940 --> 00:16:14.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">However, this time, it seems like 
someone else got the right answer.</font>

00:16:14.890 --> 00:16:18.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Hey, you provoked me. 
What's up with this old man?</i></font>

00:16:18.740 --> 00:16:24.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">More importantly, could you 
explain to me so that I can understand?</font>

00:16:24.120 --> 00:16:28.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Perhaps you should ask this girl here.</font>

00:16:28.910 --> 00:16:32.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>And now this old guy's 
making me do the hard part?!</i></font>

00:16:32.720 --> 00:16:33.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You heard him.</font>

00:16:37.520 --> 00:16:39.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In the foundation tale,</font>

00:16:39.280 --> 00:16:44.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">the Mother Royal is said to have eyes 
that can see in the darkest of nights.</font>

00:16:44.460 --> 00:16:47.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This means that those who 
are chosen by this shrine,</font>

00:16:47.070 --> 00:16:48.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">who carry the Mother Royal's bloodline,</font>

00:16:49.070 --> 00:16:52.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">have eyes that cannot tell colors apart.</font>

00:16:52.860 --> 00:16:54.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tell colors apart?</font>

00:16:54.910 --> 00:16:56.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What do you mean?</font>

00:16:56.660 --> 00:17:01.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let me explain how I chose the doors earlier.</font>

00:17:01.680 --> 00:17:04.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">First, there were three doors: 
blue, red, and green,</font>

00:17:04.750 --> 00:17:07.750
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}Do not pass through the red door</b></font>

00:17:05.310 --> 00:17:07.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">with the message, "Don't pick the red door."</font>

00:17:08.190 --> 00:17:11.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Blue and green should both be correct,</font>

00:17:11.480 --> 00:17:14.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but a child of the Mother Royal 
would choose the blue one.</font>

00:17:14.830 --> 00:17:18.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is because they would not be able 
to differentiate between red and green.</font>

00:17:18.380 --> 00:17:21.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, they would choose the door 
that they know for sure is not red.</font>

00:17:21.480 --> 00:17:24.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Cannot differentiate between red and green...</font>

00:17:24.660 --> 00:17:27.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's rare in our nation, 
but in the western region,</font>

00:17:27.710 --> 00:17:33.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">they say one in ten males are unable to 
differentiate between red and green.</font>

00:17:33.030 --> 00:17:35.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Luomen probably would have figured it out.</font>

00:17:35.900 --> 00:17:40.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Since my dad studied abroad in the west, 
he would have known about this trait.</i></font>

00:17:40.760 --> 00:17:43.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>So, that's what he meant.</i></font>

00:17:43.490 --> 00:17:45.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The same is true for the next door.</font>

00:17:45.000 --> 00:17:47.330
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}Do not pass through the brown door</b></font>

00:17:45.480 --> 00:17:47.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The instruction was to avoid the brown.</font>

00:17:47.870 --> 00:17:50.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If brown and green looked the same to a person,</font>

00:17:50.380 --> 00:17:52.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">they'd choose light blue 
through process of elimination.</font>

00:17:53.240 --> 00:17:58.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">For the last door, it said "choose red," 
yet there was no red door.</font>

00:17:54.510 --> 00:17:56.880
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20" color="#3c3e36"><b>{\an8}Choose the red door</b></font>

00:17:59.430 --> 00:18:04.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">However, if they could see 
the white and purple doors,</font>

00:18:04.740 --> 00:18:07.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">the person would assume the final door 
would have to be the red one.</font>

00:18:07.870 --> 00:18:11.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In other words, even though there 
seemed to be two correct choices,</font>

00:18:11.610 --> 00:18:15.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">there was only one truly correct answer.</font>

00:18:15.360 --> 00:18:21.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But if every emperor had such a trait, 
we would have noticed, wouldn't we?</font>

00:18:21.600 --> 00:18:25.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I heard from my adopted father that 
even if they can't tell the colors apart,</font>

00:18:25.930 --> 00:18:28.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">once they got used to it, 
they could live mostly normally.</font>

00:18:28.640 --> 00:18:31.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, it's actually quite hard 
for others to notice.</font>

00:18:31.740 --> 00:18:34.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Also, they say in exchange for 
color identification,</font>

00:18:34.590 --> 00:18:36.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">these people could see well in the dark.</font>

00:18:36.840 --> 00:18:40.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That could be what later became the legend 
of the Mother Royal's eyesight.</font>

00:18:41.070 --> 00:18:46.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So only those who had the same traits 
as the Mother Royal could pass through here.</font>

00:18:46.570 --> 00:18:50.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm sure some have made it 
through by coincidence.</font>

00:18:50.760 --> 00:18:54.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But the probability of making it through 
to the last room is very low.</font>

00:18:55.710 --> 00:19:00.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In the story, they say the Mother Royal 
came from a distant land.</font>

00:19:01.590 --> 00:19:05.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She had a trait where she 
couldn't differentiate certain colors.</font>

00:19:05.710 --> 00:19:09.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She arrived here from the west 
with many servants.</font>

00:19:10.180 --> 00:19:14.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Settling into a new land is never easy.</font>

00:19:14.160 --> 00:19:18.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Therefore, she married 
into the leadership of this land.</font>

00:19:18.370 --> 00:19:22.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wait, apothecary. The legend says 
the Mother Royal never had a husband.</font>

00:19:22.930 --> 00:19:25.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That was the clever decision 
by the Mother Royal and her family.</font>

00:19:26.770 --> 00:19:28.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's not rare to accept 
a wife from a distant land,</font>

00:19:28.640 --> 00:19:32.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">to prevent the bloodline 
from getting too thick.</font>

00:19:32.670 --> 00:19:34.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Even if the Mother Royal is the origin,</font>

00:19:34.300 --> 00:19:37.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">the imperial throne 
is held by paternal succession.</font>

00:19:37.090 --> 00:19:40.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That was probably decided to honor 
the original leader of this land.</font>

00:19:41.350 --> 00:19:48.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">However, the Mother Royal's family didn't 
want their bloodline to thin out and vanish.</font>

00:19:48.910 --> 00:19:52.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How can one make sure that 
the Mother Royal's bloodline is maintained?</font>

00:19:52.460 --> 00:19:55.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's where this Shrine of Choosing comes in.</font>

00:19:56.190 --> 00:19:59.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If no potential heir carries the trait,</i></font>

00:19:59.020 --> 00:20:03.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>a concubine from a related lineage is 
brought in to accompany them into the shrine.</i></font>

00:20:04.610 --> 00:20:08.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That's why they added the rule about 
allowing concubines to enter with the emperor.</i></font>

00:20:08.410 --> 00:20:12.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That's how they gradually infiltrated 
the center of the nation.</i></font>

00:20:13.160 --> 00:20:16.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Deep enough to chase 
the original leader out of the story</i></font>

00:20:16.480 --> 00:20:18.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>and make the Mother Royal the origin.</i></font>

00:20:18.960 --> 00:20:24.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>When nobody with first-hand knowledge 
remains, the story becomes the truth.</i></font>

00:20:24.350 --> 00:20:28.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It was a very peaceful, 
very deliberate takeover.</i></font>

00:20:28.740 --> 00:20:31.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Of course, I can't say that out loud.</i></font>

00:20:31.860 --> 00:20:36.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, are you saying that I don't carry 
the blood of the Mother Royal in me?</font>

00:20:36.410 --> 00:20:40.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This shrine is just the most 
accurate method to find out.</font>

00:20:40.800 --> 00:20:45.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sometimes, the trait is not 
passed on from parent to child.</font>

00:20:45.170 --> 00:20:49.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Also, bloodlines that become 
too thick can cause problems, too.</font>

00:20:49.080 --> 00:20:53.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That could be why the previous emperor's 
siblings all fell ill in the epidemic.</font>

00:20:54.980 --> 00:21:00.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I wouldn't have thought this 
little girl would figure it all out.</font>

00:21:00.830 --> 00:21:02.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Little girl?</i></font>

00:21:02.140 --> 00:21:04.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It is said that the Mother Royal</font>

00:21:04.660 --> 00:21:08.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">ruled over this land because 
she possessed a rare intellect.</font>

00:21:08.840 --> 00:21:14.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If you're going to thin the bloodline, 
why don't you add this one to it?</font>

00:21:14.770 --> 00:21:15.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Huh?</i></font>

00:21:16.610 --> 00:21:19.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What is this bag of bones talking about?</i></font>

00:21:19.200 --> 00:21:23.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That would be interesting, 
but I don't want to anger Lakan.</font>

00:21:23.400 --> 00:21:27.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">More importantly, she needs at least
15 centimeters more in the chest.</font>

00:21:27.420 --> 00:21:28.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Whatever.</font>

00:21:29.290 --> 00:21:31.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">However, please be careful.</font>

00:21:31.260 --> 00:21:35.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There are many who do not favorably view 
the introduction of new blood.</font>

00:21:35.950 --> 00:21:37.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, I'm aware.</font>

00:21:37.480 --> 00:21:41.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, I'm sure you are, Your Majesty.</font>

00:21:41.800 --> 00:21:43.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please be careful.</font>

00:21:46.140 --> 00:21:47.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I know.</font>

00:21:57.870 --> 00:22:00.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Who really is he?</i></font>

00:22:00.810 --> 00:22:06.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Just "the emperor's favorite eunuch?" 
That doesn't seem to add up...</i></font>

00:22:08.890 --> 00:22:10.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Well, who cares?</i></font>

